            Frequently Asked Questions 
        </p>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">1. What is the purpose of this platform?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>The purpose of our platform is to create a transparent, accessible, and user-friendly platform where individuals can report and address issues related to government schemes.</p>
            </div>
