            </div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">3. What kind of issues can be reported on this platform?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>You can report issues such as:
                    <ul>
                    <li>
                    Non-Receipt of Benefits : If you are eligible for a government scheme but have not received the benefits or support promised by the scheme.
                    </li>
                        <li>
                            Demands for bribes or illegal payments : If an intermediary, such as a government official or local agent, demands money or favors in exchange for providing the benefits of a government scheme. 
                        </li>
                        <li>
                           Ineligibility Issues : If you are wrongly deemed ineligible for a scheme despite meeting all the required criteria.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Poor Service Delivery : If the services provided under a scheme are of poor quality, incomplete, or not as promised.
                        </li>
                        
                    </ul>
                
            </div>
        </div>
